Description:
Personalized etched mason jar with your choice of design. All of our glassware can be laser etched with any design we offer or customized with one of your own. Perfect as wedding favors or that outdoor wedding.
~ITEM DETAILS~
 
-5.25 inches tall 
-Holds 16.5 ounces each 
-No lid included
-Handle comes on the left when looking at the design. Can be switched.

-Engraving is permanent and requires no maintenance 
-Each glass comes carefully packaged
~HOW TO ORDER~
1. Select the design number you want. See the 2nd image for a list of all our designs. 
2. Place your order and in the notes to seller, all the information needed for the design, i.e. names, date, initial. Please note the items you want left off.
3. Within 1 business day, we will contact you with a design proof.
~DOUBLE SIDED ETCHING~
You can now pick if you want one side engraved or two! Double sided engraving will include the design of your choice from the 2nd image and then 1 line of text on the back side. IMAGE: If you want one of our designs and an image or more than 1 line of text, you must purchase "Custom" for the design and then the two sided engraving.
~MODIFICATIONS TO THE DESIGN~
Modifications are welcome! Get it how you want it. *When adding text, charges may apply*
Name - First, last or two first names
Date - Can be omitted or can be added
Initial - (If applicable) Can be first or last initial
Title - (If applicable) For a wedding party (i.e. Groom, bridesmaid, best man) or can change to a last name, another title like ""#1 Dad"" or Happy Birthday.
~BULK ORDERING~
Pricing discounts start at orders of 12 mason jars. Please contact us for more information.
~SHIPPING~
Orders take about 3-4 days to create and 3-7 days for delivery (US) depending on the distance from Arizona. Please contact us if you need something sooner with your zip code and date needed by.
~RELATED PRODUCTS~
We offer many other products with these designs. Check out them all out here: 
https://www.etsy.com/shop/EverythingEtchedAZ?section_id=15036744
Be sure to check out our shop where we offer over 80 different designs and over 50 different products!

Description:
Personalised Tie Clip Personalized Wedding Gift Custom Stamped Ushers Best Man Groomsmen Valentines Gift Boyfriend Gift   in Gift Box
 A great addition for the gentleman in your life, the perfect embellishment to a smart suit.  
A great gift for the Best Man, Ushers or the Father of the Groom and Bride and the Groom himself
Can be personalised with a name, initials or a very short message, maybe even the co-ordinates of a special place.  
Great for a 10th Wedding Anniversary gift
**We recommend up to 20 characters to be stamped to the front of the tie clip and up to 10 characters to the back, that includes any spaces. **
The clip is made of aluminium and is stamped and shaped by us here. it measures approximately 6cm.
Supplied in a rustic gift box
We have more tie clips in our shop here:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/HandstampedWotNots?ref=hdr_shop_menu§ion_id=17474576
Please leave the details of your personalisation in the note to seller box at checkout.  Thank you.
Handstamping involves striking metal with steel stamps by hand and, therefore, there will probably be a slight impression on the reverse side of the item. Any quirks and irregularities  are part of the process, letters may not line up evenly and spacing can vary so can the depth of each letter.
These are not considered defects. Rather they add to the charm of each piece,when you receive your item, there will be no other quite the same, truly one of a kind, as no two pieces are ever exactly the same, yours will be totally unique to you.
